  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales Executive (Car Accessories)",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>An Automotive Enthusiast </strong></em><br /><em><strong>Basic Plus Attractive Commission & Incentive</strong></em></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Specialize and handle sales for automotive vehicle parts and accessories.</li><li>To maintain strong relationships with existing customers and partners to increase sales.</li><li>Strive to achieve and exceed monthly sales targets.</li><li>Attend to and listen to customers’ sales enquiries and provide solutions to their needs on car accessories.</li><li>Explain the benefits of aftermarket accessories to customers.</li><li>Follow up with customers and provide after-sales support.</li><li>Keep abreast of the new and latest automotive products and accessories.</li><li>Maintain and manage in-house accessories inventory.</li><li>Liaise and update the Service Advisors on the latest accessories and pricing.</li><li>Engage with distributors at the dealership on discounts and rebates based on performance quota.</li><li>Work with designers to develop marketing materials.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Min 2 years of Car Accessories sales working experience</li><li>Diploma or equivalent, or relevant years of related working experience.</li><li>Enjoy talking to people. Motivated and positive attitude</li><li>Able to prospect via phone, email, and direct selling.</li><li>Good persuasion, negotiation, and closing skills.</li><li>Patience in dealing with customers and calls.</li><li>Ability to handle sales targets and achieve KPIs within deadlines.</li><li>Knowledge of social media marketing & managing online marketplaces (eg, Shopee/Lazada)</li><li>Singaporean applicants only</li><li>Workplace in Sin Ming area</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><br /></p>",
