    "description": "<p>Incorporated in Singapore in the year 2012, OPTIMA WERKZ Pte Ltd is a one-stop premier after-market automotive service provider in Singapore offering comprehensive and integrated automotive related solutions to customers.</p>\n<p>The Optima Werkz team comprises of professionally-trained senior technicians who are able to diagnose, identify and rectify the faults on various makes and models of premium continental and Japanese cars. Our expertise extends across a wide range of makes and models of passenger cars in Singapore, including luxury passenger cars and ultra-luxury supercars.</p>",
